intent.user_query: What is the average resolution time for service requests, broken down by service request type, and show only service requests resolved in under 7 days?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT ServiceType, AVG(CAST((ResolutionDate - RequestDate) AS INTEGER)) AS AverageResolutionTimeInDays FROM fitness_db.ServiceRequests WHERE (ResolutionDate - RequestDate) < 7 GROUP BY ServiceType;

arguments.sql: SELECT ServiceType, AVG(CAST((ResolutionDate - RequestDate) AS INTEGER)) AS AverageResolutionTimeInDays FROM fitness_db.ServiceRequests WHERE (ResolutionDate - RequestDate) < 7 GROUP BY ServiceType;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
